snippet.title: Mantra-NextFest Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Humanity is on the brink of extinction. Corrupted AI code caused thousands of industrial robots to turn into human-killing murder machines. As the former lead developer for Tenso Corp, you feel it's your duty to right the wrongs that brought chaos to the world.

Steam Page - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1994700/Mantra/

RubyShark Games Website - https://www.rubysharkgames.com/

Discord - https://discord.gg/G9sQqfKC
